# Minimal Mistakes theme

Forked from https://github.com/mmistakes/minimal-mistakes.

Main changes:
- Deleted some files and folders
    .editorconfig
    .gitattributes
    .github
    /docs
    /test
    CHANGELOG.md
    minimal-mistakes-jekyll.gemspec
    README.md
    screenshot-layouts.png
    screenshot.png
- Gemfile
- config.yml

To add a new page, create a file these info:
    title: "Audio files"
    layout: single
    permalink: /path
    author_profile: false
and update the navigation.yml accordingly:
    parent_page:
  - title: "Your page Title"
    url: https://yourname.github.io/path


No underscore for folder names

To modify the homepage content, either modify index.html or replace it by another file.